'''約瑟·基斯杜化·"祖"·列特利'''（{{lang-en|'''Joseph Christopher "Joe" Ledley'''}}，{{bd|1987年|1月21日|catidx=Ledley, Joe}}）出生於[[威爾斯|威爾斯]][[加的夫|加的夫]]，是一名已退役[[威爾斯人|威爾斯]]職業足球員，場上主要司職[[中場|中場]]，可擔任正中場或左中場，亦曾串演[[後衛_(足球)#邊後衛|左閘]]。他曾是[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯國家隊]]國腳。

==生平==
===早年===
列特利在[[加的夫|加的夫]]出生，於[[Fairwater,_Cardiff|费尔沃特]]（Fairwater）地區長大，就讀於「坎頓尼安高校」（Cantonian High School），他的照片現時仍掛在校內<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/wales/7334999.stm |title=Local hero Ledley reaps rewards |publisher=''[[BBC|BBC News]]'' |date=2008-04-08 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2008-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080412024010/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/wales/7334999.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 球會 ===
==== 卡迪夫城 ====
列特利自9歲加入從小已支持的家鄉球隊[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]，透過青訓系統由少年隊經歷青訓學院、優材中心而於17歲晉身一隊，在擔任學徒球員的後期，他負責清潔時任球隊[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[格拉汉姆·卡瓦纳吉|格拉汉姆·卡瓦纳吉]]的球靴<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2006/09/13/when-ledley-took-a-shine-to-kav-91466-17738493/ |title=When Ledley took a shine to Kav |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=2006-09-13 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2011-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810220801/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2006/09/13/when-ledley-took-a-shine-to-kav-91466-17738493/ }}</ref>。

[[2004年至2005年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2004/05年球季]]季初列特利獲徵召晉身一隊，於2004年9月21日在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第二圈作客4-1擊敗[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米爾頓凱恩斯]]處子上陣；而10月16日主場2-0擊敗[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|洛達咸]]是其首次在聯賽登場。11月3日列特利在主場4-1擊敗[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]取得首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3967405.stm |title=Cardiff 4-1 West Ham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-11-03 |accessdate=2011-01-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304225734/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3967405.stm }}</ref>；首季在各項賽事上陣32場及射入3球。[[2005年至2006年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|翌季]]他上陣44場及射入4球。[[2006年至2007年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2006/07年球季]]列特利在全部46場聯賽正選上陣，雖然只射入3球，但在2006年8月5日揭幕戰2-1擊敗[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]他先拔頭籌<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/5226748.stm |title=Barnsley 1-2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-08-05 |accessdate=2011-01-03 |archive-date=2021-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009073958/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/5226748.stm }}</ref>，為他贏得「[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英格蘭聯賽]]年度金球」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/6417713.stm |title=Gunter and Ledley secure prizes |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-03-05 |accessdate=2011-01-03 |archive-date=2007-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071229050737/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/6417713.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2007年10月列特利與卡迪夫城續簽兩年新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7022924.stm |title=Ledley extends Cardiff contract |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-10-02 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2021-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211116104717/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7022924.stm }}</ref>，11月13日他首次獲選「威爾斯球會年度最佳球員」（Welsh Clubman of the year）<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7093725.stm |title=Bellamy nets Welsh player award |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-11-13 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2022-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220417083816/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7093725.stm }}</ref>。同年12月[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]提出初步250萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，連同附帶條件可增加到350萬英鎊希望羅致旗下，但被他一口拒絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.expressandstar.com/latest/2007/12/22/wolves-fail-in-25m-bid/ |title=Wolves fail in £2.5m bid |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-12-22 |accessdate=2011-01-06}}</ref>；而傳聞[[英超|英超]]球會[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]亦有意出價350萬英鎊爭購<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailypost.co.uk/sport-news/everton-fc/2008/01/04/everton-face-battle-for-joe-ledley-55578-20311957/ |title=Everton face battle for Joe Ledley |publisher=''dailypost.co.uk'' |date=2008-01-04 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314092451/http://www.dailypost.co.uk/sport-news/everton-fc/2008/01/04/everton-face-battle-for-joe-ledley-55578-20311957/ |archivedate=2012-03-14 }}</ref>，直到[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉，卡迪夫城董事會仍然不為巨額轉會費所動<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/01/31/bluebirds-boss-fends-off-big-money-offers-91466-20418043/ |title=Bluebirds boss fends off big money offers |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=2008-01-31 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2011-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810220834/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/01/31/bluebirds-boss-fends-off-big-money-offers-91466-20418043/ }}</ref>。於轉會傳聞中列特利在1月份射入4球，獲選「英冠1月份最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7229051.stm |title=Ledley chosen for January award |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-02-05 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2020-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602184918/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7229051.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。列特利在2008年3月初因[[腿後腱|腿後腱]]受傷而缺席包括[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]半準決賽淘汰[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]等數場賽事。他於足總盃準決賽在[[溫布萊球場|新溫布萊]]對另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]及時傷癒復出，並於開賽後9分鐘射入全場賽事唯一入球，協助卡迪夫城自1927年以來首次晉級決賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7326118.stm |title=Barnsley 0-1 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-04-06 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2009-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307133725/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7326118.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並獲選足總盃準決賽「每圈最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7342501.stm |title=Team of the FA Cup 2007/08 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-04-15 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2020-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602185326/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7342501.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在決賽不敵[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]只能屈局亞軍<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7393770.stm |title=Portsmouth 1-0 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-05-17 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608221453/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7393770.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]對列特利而言可稱大豐收，為卡迪夫城在各項賽事合共射入11球而與[[保罗·帕里|保罗·帕里]]（Paul Parry）併列球會首席神射手。

2008年9月1日夏季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前，新升[[英超|英超]]的[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]盡最後努力，由之前數月的250萬英鎊出價逐步增加到據報達600萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]求購列特利，但仍被卡迪夫城所拒<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/09/02/ledley-stays-but-cardiff-are-smarting-over-smertin-91466-21651632/ |title=Ledley stays, but Cardiff smart over Smertin |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=2008-09-02 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2009-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090414125350/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/09/02/ledley-stays-but-cardiff-are-smarting-over-smertin-91466-21651632/ }}</ref>。10月7日列特利連續第二年獲選「威爾斯球會年度最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7658105.stm |title=Davies wins Welsh player award |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-10-07 |accessdate=2011-01-06}}</ref>。11月15日主場對[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]，列特利射入他在[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2008/09年球季]]首個入球兼2-1獲勝的奠勝球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7711436.stm |title=Cardiff 2-1 Crystal Palace |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-11-15 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2019-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628234514/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7711436.stm }}</ref>，賽事中他因手指[[脫臼|脫臼]]需要離場治理，賽後需要接受[[手術|手術]]用釘固定手指，預計缺陣1個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7733546.stm |title=Ledley has pins placed in finger |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-11-18 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2017-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921101241/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7733546.stm }}</ref>。但他配帶手指套趕及在11月30日作客在[[自由球場|-{zh-hans:自由球场; zh-hk:自由球場;}-]]出戰[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7754131.stm |title=Ledley passed fit for Welsh derby |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-11-28 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2017-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921100057/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7754131.stm }}</ref>，是雙方近9年來首次碰頭，他於半場重開後以左腳「窩利」射入扳平1-1，最終在各有一人被逐下雙方2-2平手完場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7747659.stm |title=Swansea 2-2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-11-30 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402165342/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7747659.stm }}</ref>，這個入球其後獲選球會的「年度金球」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/04/27/cardiff-city-supporters-club-roll-call-of-honour-91466-23478829/ |title=Cardiff City Supporters Club Roll Call Of Honour |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=2009-04-27 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2009-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630042101/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/04/27/cardiff-city-supporters-club-roll-call-of-honour-91466-23478829/ }}</ref>。在這場「南威爾斯打吡」（South Wales derby）下一場賽事，於12月6日主場2-0擊敗[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]，[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[达伦·普尔斯|达伦·普尔斯]]（Darren Purse）缺陣，而副隊長[[斯蒂芬·麦克菲尔|斯蒂芬·麦克菲尔]]（Stephen McPhail）又在上場被逐罰停賽，年僅21歲的列特利獲派帶上隊長臂章<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~1478648,00.html |title=TEAMS: JOE LE CAPTAIN |publisher=[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|''cardiffcityfc.co.uk'']] |date=2008-12-06 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309171200/http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10335~1478648%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-03-09 }}</ref>。他在1月份再有優異的演出，獲選「英冠1月份最佳球員」，距離上次獲獎剛好一年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7881097.stm |title=Ledley named player of the month |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-02-09 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002101844/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7881097.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於1月[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]卡迪夫城拒絕兩單[[英超|英超]]球會的收購要求，包括[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]的出價500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/01/26/cardiff-city-reject-5m-west-ham-bid-for-joe-ledley-91466-22777443/ |title=Cardiff City reject 5m West Ham bid for Joe Ledley |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=2009-01-26 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2009-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090409023417/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/01/26/cardiff-city-reject-5m-west-ham-bid-for-joe-ledley-91466-22777443/ }}</ref>，及[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]的400萬英鎊現金加前卡迪夫城球員兼[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯國腳]][[贾森·库马斯|高馬斯]]同樣被拒<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-news/2009/01/27/cardiff-city-turn-down-koumas-swap-with-ledley-91466-22784590/ |title=Cardiff City turn down Koumas swap with Ledley |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2009-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090409021934/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-news/2009/01/27/cardiff-city-turn-down-koumas-swap-with-ledley-91466-22784590/ }}</ref>。他在餘下球季繼續擔任隊長之職，並於季末與隊友[[罗杰·约翰逊|-{zh-hans:罗杰·约翰逊; zh-hk:羅渣·莊臣;}-]]（Roger Johnson）一同入選[[PFA年度最佳陣容|2008/09年度PFA英冠年度最佳陣容]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/News/ChampionshipNewsDetail/0,,10794~1640656,00.html |title=Championship team of the year |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |date=2009-04-27 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430042004/http://www.football-league.co.uk/page/News/ChampionshipNewsDetail/0%2C%2C10794~1640656%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-04-30 }}</ref>。

由於只餘一年合約在身，球季結束後列特利的去向傳聞四起，主要與[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]拉上關係，其時任領隊[[菲爾·布朗|菲爾·布朗]]（Phil Brown）更出席卡迪夫城在季前對[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]的[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8164021.stm |title=Cardiff City 0-0 Celtic |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-07-22 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413080808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8164021.stm }}</ref>，列特利在這場[[卡迪夫城運動場|卡迪夫城運動場]]揭幕戰上半場上陣45分鐘。在[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2009/10年球季]]第三場聯賽是列特利為卡迪夫城上陣第200場聯賽，以3-1擊敗[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]。2009年9月2日卡迪夫城向他提供一份四年新約，但其後被列特利拒絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12874_5531472,00.html |title=Ledley offered a new contract |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2 September 2009 |accessdate=2 September 2009 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XYiD8JD?url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12874_5531472,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月26日於1-3負於[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，他接獲兩面[[黃牌|黃牌]]，生涯首次遭[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8263782.stm |title=Sheff Wed 3–1 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=26 September 2009 |accessdate=26 September 2009 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XYjLWj6?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8263782.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。列特利由於髖部受傷而影響演出<ref>{{Cite web |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2009/12/02/joe-ledley-i-need-hip-surgery-91466-25299633/ |title=Joe Ledley: I need hip surgery |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=2 December 2009 |accessdate=7 December 2009 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XYmaA6b?url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city/cardiff-city-fc/2009/12/02/joe-ledley-i-need-hip-surgery-91466-25299633/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於12月9日卡迪夫城證實需在球季結束前接受[[手術|手術]]治理<ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8404373.stm |title=Cardiff City star Joe Ledley 'needs hip operation' |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=9 December 2009 |accessdate=9 December 2009 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XYnv0gV?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8404373.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於2010年1月29日開刀，初時預計缺席餘下的球季<ref>{{Cite web |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-news/2010/01/30/stoke-s-gerry-francis-runs-rule-over-joe-ledley-91466-25718032/ |title=Stoke's Gerry Francis runs rule over Joe Ledley |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=30 January 2010 |accessdate=15 February 2010 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XYq3Ayv?url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-news/2010/01/30/stoke-s-gerry-francis-runs-rule-over-joe-ledley-91466-25718032/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他在4月3日2-1擊敗[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]提前復出，以後補身份上陣接近30分鐘<ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8594829.stm |title=Cardiff 2–1 Swansea |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=3 April 2010 |accessdate=17 April 2010 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XYr1HeH?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8594829.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月17日列特利在作客射入奠勝球1-0擊敗[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]全取寶貴3分，協助卡迪夫城以聯賽第4位結束球季參加升班附加賽，準決賽兩回合累3-3，需要憑[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]才以4-3淘汰[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]，列特利負責已隊第三球十二碼中的<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8672579.stm |title=Cardiff 2-3 Leicester (agg 3-3) |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-12 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2010-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100513031928/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8672579.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月22日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]決賽對[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，列特利射入1球為球賽再度領先2-1，但最終2-3敗陣無緣升班<ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8692465.stm |title=Blackpool 3–2 Cardiff |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=22 May 2010 |accessdate=23 May 2010 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XYsASwg?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8692465.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這亦是他為卡迪夫城最後一場上陣。

==== 些路迪 ====
列特利與[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]的合約於[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2009/10年球季]]後屆滿，他與包括[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]、[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]、[[羅馬足球俱樂部|羅馬]]等數支球隊展開談判<ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/3040849/Stoke-offer-Michael-Tonge-in-Joe-Ledley-deal.html |title=Tonge twist in Led hunt |publisher=''thesun.co.uk'' |date=5 July 2010 |accessdate=12 July 2010 |archive-date=2012-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020123815/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/3040849/Stoke-offer-Michael-Tonge-in-Joe-Ledley-deal.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/celtic/8714916.stm |title=Cardiff's Joe Ledley will travel to AS Roma for talks |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=1 June 2010|accessdate=12 July 2010}}</ref>，最終在2010年7月12日與[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]達成協議簽署四年合約<ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2010/07/12/joe-ledley-completes-celtic-move-91466-26835003/ |title=Joe Ledley completes Celtic move |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=12 July 2010 |accessdate=12 July 2010}}</ref>，由於轉投脫離[[英格蘭足球聯賽系統|英格蘭足球聯賽系統]]的球會，卡迪夫城不能收取陪養補償金，變成人財兩失<ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2010/07/10/fifa-brought-into-joe-ledley-wrangle-91466-26822333/ |title=FIFA brought into Joe Ledley wrangle |publisher=''walesonline.co.uk'' |date=10 July 2010 |accessdate=10 July 2010 |archive-date=2010-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100917004105/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2010/07/10/fifa-brought-into-joe-ledley-wrangle-91466-26822333/ }}</ref>。他於7月28日[[歐聯|歐聯]][[2010/11歐洲冠軍聯賽外圍賽及附加賽#外圍賽第三圈|外圍賽]]首回合作客0-3負於[[布拉加體育會|布拉加]]首次上陣<ref>{{Cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/celtic/8860029.stm |title=Braga 3–0 Celtic |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=28 July 2010 |accessdate=29 July 2010 |archive-date=2010-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100728190241/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/celtic/8860029.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，然後於8月14日作客1-0擊敗[[因弗内斯足球俱乐部|恩華尼斯]]作[[蘇超|蘇超]]處子演出<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8909529.stm |title=Inverness CT 0-1 Celtic |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-14 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2021-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211116110342/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8909529.stm }}</ref>；8月22日主場4-0擊敗[[圣米伦足球俱乐部|聖美倫]]列特利先拔頭籌兼取得加盟後首球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8930126.stm |title=Celtic 4-0 St Mirren |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-22 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2012-12-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ch9iFupQ?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8930126.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月16日些路迪破記錄在主場以9-0大勝[[阿伯丁足球俱乐部|鴨巴甸]]，列特利亦射入1球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/9161840.stm |title=Celtic 9-0 Aberdeen |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-16 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2012-07-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68te0LH99?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/9161840.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國家隊 ===
列特利在青少年時期代表[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]參加數個不同年齡級別的國際賽，於2005年9月7日不足19歲首次代表[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯成年隊]]上陣，於[[2006年世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|世界盃外圍賽]]作客出戰[[波蘭國家足球隊|波蘭]]。2007年10月17日在[[2008年欧洲足球锦标赛外围赛|2008年歐國盃外圍賽]]作客對[[聖馬利諾國家足球隊|聖馬利諾]]取得首個國際賽入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7044147.stm |title=San Marino 1-2 Wales |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-10-17 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2013-02-12 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EMhU9s8H?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7044147.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年5月29日由於多名浦規正選因傷退隊，年僅22歲的列特利首次帶上[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]臂章，帶領一支歷來最年青，平均只有21歲的國家隊迎戰世界排名113的[[愛沙尼亞國家足球隊|愛沙尼亞]]，隊中7名正選仍有資格代表U21上陣，結果憑隊中最老資格的[[羅拔·安梳爾|安梳爾]]（Robert Earnshaw）射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]以1-0取勝<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/fulham/8046478.stm |title=Wales 1-0 Estonia |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-05-29 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2018-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215231402/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/fulham/8046478.stm }}</ref>；而其後一場[[2010年世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|世界盃外圍賽]]作客[[巴库|巴库]]對[[阿塞拜疆國家足球隊|阿塞拜疆]]，列特利繼續擔任隊長<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8075370.stm |title=Azerbaijan 0-1 Wales |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-06-06 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-date=2011-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110203053538/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8075370.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

